<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/common.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>각각가각구툐페이지</h1>
    <div>투표타이틀 <%= voting.title  %></div>
    <div>투표설명 <%= voting.description  %></div>
    <div>만료날자 <%= voting.expiration  %></div>
